2026-06-01T11:09:03.2042846Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2043519Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2044099Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2044888Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2045610Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2046302Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2047279Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2047987Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2048659Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2049316Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2049811Z 33    -->
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2050322Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2051250Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2052244Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
