2026-06-01T11:09:03.2658933Z 247            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2659706Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2660703Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2661366Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2662010Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2662786Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2663508Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2664209Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-06-01T11:09:03.2664796Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
